        Parameters:
        productName - String, it represents the name of the serie.
        movieDirector - String, it represents the director of the serie.
        synopsis - String, it represents an abstract of the serie.
        day - int, it represents the opening day of the serie.
        month - int, it represents the opening month of the serie.
        year - int, it represents the opening year of the serie.
        censoredSerie - boolean, if censoredSerie = true the serie has been censored else the series has not been censored.
        razonCensored - String, if censoredSerie = true, it represents the censored reason why the serie was censored.
        numActors - int, it represents the amount of actors of the serie
        scheduledEpisodes - int, it represents the amount of scheduled episodes of the serie.
        publishedEpisodes - int,it represents the amount of published episodes of the serie.
        pathTrailer - String, it represents the link of the thrailer of the serie.
        auxActors - String [], it represents an array that contains the name of the main actors of the serie.
